<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 00:33:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>开车时不要幽默：美国禁止在高速公路电子信号上显示有趣的信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/no-to-humour-while-driving-us-to-ban-funny-messages-on-highway-e-signals/articleshow/106879542.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106879542.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国联邦公路管理局已给各州两年时间禁止在高架电子标志上显示幽默和古怪的信息。禁止发布含义晦涩、涉及流行文化或搞笑的消息。这是因为可能会造成误解或分散驾驶员的注意力。那些即将消失的信息包括马萨诸塞州的“Use Yah Blinkah”等信息； “拜访姻亲？慢点，晚点去”，来自俄亥俄州等地。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 23:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/no-to-humour-while-driving-us-to-ban-funny-messages-on-highway-e-signals/articleshow/106879542.cms</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞叛军在红海向美国军舰发射导弹，这是美国领导的袭击后的首次袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthifired-missile-strikes-usowned-vessel-in-gulf-of-aden-raising-tensions/articleshow/106879352.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106879352.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 23:20:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthifired-missile-strikes-usowned-vessel-in-gulf-of-aden-raising-tensions/articleshow/106879352.cms</guid></item><item><title>反贫困组织乐施会表示，世界可能在 10 年内出现第一位万亿富翁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/the-worlds-first-trillionaire-a-report-by-oxfam-international/articleshow/106879330.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106879330.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 23:15:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/the-worlds-first-trillionaire-a-report-by-oxfam-international/articleshow/106879330.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜金正恩呼吁改变韩国地位并警告战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-calls-for-change-in-status-of-south-warns-of-war/articleshow/106878271.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106878271.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;观察人士认为，朝鲜最近对韩国立场的变化反映了现实，并可能最终有助于朝韩关系正常化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 22:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-calls-for-change-in-status-of-south-warns-of-war/articleshow/106878271.cms</guid></item><item><title>飞机坠入太平洋后正在进行搜索行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/airplane-crashes-into-pacific-ocean-in-bay-south-of-san-franciso/articleshow/106876509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106876509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一架飞机在旧金山南部机场附近坠入太平洋。半月湾的搜索行动正在进行中。事件发生在距离半月湾机场几英里的地方。包括美国海岸警卫队和消防人员在内的多个当局已赶赴现场。目前尚不清楚机上人员和具体飞机的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 20:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/airplane-crashes-into-pacific-ocean-in-bay-south-of-san-franciso/articleshow/106876509.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国官员表示，伊拉克的导弹袭击并未影响美国设施</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/missile-strikes-in-iraq-did-not-affect-us-facilities-say-us-officials-latest-news/articleshow/106878124.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106878124.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 22:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/missile-strikes-in-iraq-did-not-affect-us-facilities-say-us-officials-latest-news/articleshow/106878124.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着更多油轮避开，也门胡塞武装威胁袭击美国船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/yemens-houthis-threaten-to-hit-us-ships-as-more-tankers-steer-clear/articleshow/106876140.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106876140.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于红海袭击导致船只暂停或改道，补给线受到影响。由于袭击推迟了日本制造的发动机的抵达，汽车制造商铃木停止了在匈牙利的生产。对能源市场的影响有限，欧洲天然气价格下跌，石油价格小幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 19:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/yemens-houthis-threaten-to-hit-us-ships-as-more-tankers-steer-clear/articleshow/106876140.cms</guid></item><item><title>差点斩首英属印度女友的突尼斯寻求庇护者被拘留在精神病院</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/tunisian-asylum-seeker-who-nearly-beheaded-british-indian-girlfriend-detained-in-psychiatric-hospital/articleshow/106875405.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106875405.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名突尼斯寻求庇护者在伦敦大学宿舍杀害并差点斩首其 19 岁英属印度学生女友萨比塔·坦瓦尼 (Sabita Thanwani)，之后被无限期拘留在布罗德莫戒备森严的精神病医院。老贝利听说马赫·马鲁夫（24 岁）于 2022 年 3 月 19 日在塔瓦尼位于城市大学附近 Arbor House 的房间里杀死了塔瓦尼，她是城市大学心理学专业的本科生，前途光明。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 18:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/tunisian-asylum-seeker-who-nearly-beheaded-british-indian-girlfriend-detained-in-psychiatric-hospital/articleshow/106875405.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着 2024 年总统竞选在爱荷华州拉开帷幕，美国各地持续出现危险的寒冷天气</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/dangerously-cold-temperatures-continue-across-us-as-2024-presidential-race-begins-in-iowa/articleshow/106874837.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106874837.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北极爆炸继续在美国各地造成严重破坏，导致北部各州和德克萨斯州的众多客户停电。这种极端天气条件也可能影响爱荷华州的选民投票率，即将举行的总统竞选的第一批共和党候选人选票将于 11 月进行。美国国家气象局（NWS）警告称，危险的寒冷天气将持续一整天。恶劣的天气导致北部各州和德克萨斯州数万人停电。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/dangerously-cold-temperatures-continue-across-us-as-2024-presidential-race-begins-in-iowa/articleshow/106874837.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿拉斯加航空公司发生井喷事故后，波音公司将加强对 737-Max 的检查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/boeing-to-increase-quality-inspections-on-737-max-following-alaska-airlines-blow-out/articleshow/106874207.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106874207.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波音公司周一通知员工，继上周阿拉斯加航空航班紧急出口门板出现故障后，该公司打算扩大对其 737 Max 9 飞机的质量检查。此次检查是在联邦当局对 737 Max 进行停飞之后进行的，波音公司表示，阿拉斯加航空的航班和客户投诉表明，在质量保证和控制方面，“我们没有达到我们需要达到的目标”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 16:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/boeing-to-increase-quality-inspections-on-737-max-following-alaska-airlines-blow-out/articleshow/106874207.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰总统与政府在解雇国家检察官问题上存在分歧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/polands-president-and-government-at-odds-over-dismissal-of-state-prosecutor/articleshow/106864294.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106864294.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总统一名高级助手周一辩称，波兰司法部长不公正地解雇了国家检察官达里乌什·巴尔斯基(Dariusz Barski)，在总统和新政府之间的斗争中建立了一条新战线。司法部长亚当·博德纳尔 (Adam Bodnar) 的任务是撤销前民族主义法律和司法 (PiS) 政府实施的改革，批评者声称该改革对司法机构的政治影响力增加。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:25:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/polands-president-and-government-at-odds-over-dismissal-of-state-prosecutor/articleshow/106864294.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国宣布数十年来最大规模的军事部署参加北约演习</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-announces-largest-military-deployment-to-nato-exercises-in-decades/articleshow/106870978.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106870978.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国国防部长格兰特·沙普斯周一宣布，英国将派遣 2 万名武装部队人员参加北约自冷战以来最大规模的演习之一，并对西方领导的联盟面临的日益增长的威胁表示担忧。在该军事联盟的“坚定捍卫者演习”期间，英国皇家空军、皇家海军和陆军的人员将与其他31个成员国以及北约申请国瑞典的人员联手。沙普斯在谈到上周针对伊朗支持的胡塞叛军的英美联合行动时表示，这些行动的目的是“作为单一行动”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-announces-largest-military-deployment-to-nato-exercises-in-decades/articleshow/106870978.cms</guid></item><item><title>女孩们受到英国美容团伙的“摆布”：评论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/failings-by-police-and-councils-left-girls-at-mercy-of-uk-grooming-gangs-review/articleshow/106865745.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106865745.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一项独立调查显示，英格兰北部警察和议会负责人的失职导致女孩多年来一直受到恋童癖诱骗团伙的摆布。该审查突显了大曼彻斯特警方对罗奇代尔虐待事件的多次调查失败，原因是资源不足且缺乏对施虐者的逮捕。该报告证实了两名举报人的清白——危机干预小组的协调员和侦探玛吉·奥利弗。这项审查是在一部关于两名举报人的纪录片之后委托进行的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 11:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/failings-by-police-and-councils-left-girls-at-mercy-of-uk-grooming-gangs-review/articleshow/106865745.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么许多船只在红海显示“全中国”标识</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-many-ships-are-displaying-all-chinese-identity-in-red-sea/articleshow/106865327.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106865327.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;至少有九艘船只在接近或穿越红海时更改了其自动识别系统（AIS），以显示“中文”或“全部中文”等信息。该系统是国际海事公约规定的全球跟踪器。这种新做法表明，船东或船员认为，展示与中国的联系可能会让他们显得对加沙巴勒斯坦人或胡塞武装表示同情，后者自11月以来在红海加剧了袭击。这与北京方面将中国描绘成在全球冲突中保持中立的民族主义主张是一致的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 11:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-many-ships-are-displaying-all-chinese-identity-in-red-sea/articleshow/106865327.cms</guid></item><item><title>暂时获释的伊朗记者因藐视头巾而面临新的法律诉讼</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-journalists-temporarily-released-face-new-legal-case-for-flouting-hijab/articleshow/106864920.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106864920.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗司法机构米赞周一报道称，伊朗司法机构对两名被监禁的女记者立案，原因是她们在暂时出狱后未戴头巾。 Niloofar Hamedi 和 Elaheh Mohammadi 因报道 2022 年库尔德裔伊朗人 Mahsa Amini 在拘留期间死亡事件而分别被判处 13 年和 12 年监禁，周日在支付保释后暂时获释。米赞说：“被告不戴头巾的视频在网上发布后，针对他们提起了新的诉讼。”他指的是社交媒体上广泛分享的一段视频。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-journalists-temporarily-released-face-new-legal-case-for-flouting-hijab/articleshow/106864920.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将升级南海争议地区的前哨基地</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippines-to-upgrade-outposts-in-disputed-south-china-sea/articleshow/106862870.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106862870.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾军事参谋长周一表示，菲律宾将升级其沿海水域的前哨基地，并采购更多船只，以反击中国在有争议的南中国海日益增强的自信。马尼拉和北京在该航道上存在领土争端由来已久，但最近两国船只发生的一系列事件导致两国关系急剧恶化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:44:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippines-to-upgrade-outposts-in-disputed-south-china-sea/articleshow/106862870.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其释放加沙战争争端中的以色列足球运动员</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-releases-israeli-footballer-in-gaza-war-spat/articleshow/106862887.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106862887.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其法院释放了以色列足球运动员萨吉夫·耶赫兹克尔 (Sagiv Jehezkel)，他因展示有关以色列-哈马斯战争的信息而被拘留。耶赫兹克尔展示了一条绷带，上面写着“100 天”。 07/10&amp;#39; 和一场比赛中的大卫之星。关于绷带的声明提到了周日庆祝的以色列与哈马斯战争的第 100 天。该事件使以色列和土耳其之间的关系变得紧张。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-releases-israeli-footballer-in-gaza-war-spat/articleshow/106862887.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦选举委员会告诉参议院，2月8日的投票不能推迟</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/resolution-to-delay-february-8-polls-in-pakistan-senate-islamabad-news/articleshow/106861970.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106861970.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦选举委员会拒绝参议院寻求推迟大选的决议，称所有安排均已完成。委员会已发布加强安全并为和平选举创造适宜环境的指示。现阶段不建议推迟选举。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:24:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/resolution-to-delay-february-8-polls-in-pakistan-senate-islamabad-news/articleshow/106861970.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其士兵在伊拉克阵亡后因“赞扬恐怖主义”而拘留了18人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-holds-18-people-for-praising-terrorism-after-soldiers-killed-in-iraq/articleshow/106861606.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106861606.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当局周一表示，土耳其警方在上周杀害士兵后以“赞扬恐怖主义”为由拘留了 18 人，而一名被取缔的库尔德工人党 (PKK) 高级成员在伊拉克北部被“消灭”。周五，九名土耳其士兵在伊拉克北部与库尔德工人党的冲突中丧生，促使安卡拉在伊拉克北部和叙利亚北部进行空袭和行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-holds-18-people-for-praising-terrorism-after-soldiers-killed-in-iraq/articleshow/106861606.cms</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国禁令，中国军方和政府仍采购英伟达芯片</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-military-and-government-acquire-nvidia-chips-despite-us-ban/articleshow/106864326.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106864326.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管美国对英伟达半导体向中国出口施加限制，但路透社对招标文件的审查显示，中国军事实体、人工智能研究机构和大学在过去一年中继续购买被禁芯片。这突显了美国在限制中国获得先进芯片方面面临的挑战，以及尽管替代品已经开发出来，但中国人工智能领域对英伟达产品的持续需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-military-and-government-acquire-nvidia-chips-despite-us-ban/articleshow/106864326.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>